item.title: Conference Rooms Teams App.
item.description:
To enhance the security of your Teams account, we've implemented a new login procedure for the conference rooms.
This step-by-step guide will help protect your sensitive data from unauthorized access.
Step 1:

If the computer was logged out in the previous session, log in using the following credentials:
Username: kevinl
Password: gsg08kevinL
Step 2:

Double-click on the 'ClearTeamsCreds' shortcut on the desktop. A "User Account Control" window should open. Click "yes"


Step 3:

Open Microsoft Teams as you normally would.

Step 4 IMPORTANT:

After entering your Microsoft username and password, you will see the following window. This step is crucial, select the option 'No, sign in to this app only.'

Step 5:

"Sign Out" of Teams as usual.

Step 6:

Once again double click on the "ClearTeamsCreds" shortcut on the desktop.
